'''硝酸钇'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Y(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它的受热分解经YONO<sub>3</sub>，最终生成[[氧化钇|Y<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=86|issue=1|language=en|date=1990-5|pages=125–128|doi=10.1016/0022-4596(90)90122-E|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/002245969090122E|title=A study on reaction mechanism in preparation of Y-Ba-Cu-O superconducting material from the thermoreaction method of nitrates|accessdate=2019-03-16|author=R.F. Zhuang, J.B. Qiu, Y.P. Zhu|archive-date=2018-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610144557/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/002245969090122E|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==制备==
硝酸钇可由[[氧化钇|氧化钇]]和[[硝酸|硝酸]]反应得到：<ref name="DongHua2014">{{cite journal|last1=Dong|first1=Bin|last2=Hua|first2=Rui N.|last3=Cao|first3=Bao S.|last4=Li|first4=Zhi P.|last5=He|first5=Yang Y.|last6=Zhang|first6=Zhen Y.|last7=Wolfbeis|first7=Otto S.|title=Size dependence of the upconverted luminescence of NaYF4:Er,Yb microspheres for use in ratiometric thermometry|journal=Physical Chemistry Chemical Physics|volume=16|issue=37|year=2014|pages=20009–12|issn=1463-9076|doi=10.1039/C4CP01966K|pmid=25123272|bibcode=2014PCCP...1620009D}}</ref>
: Y<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + 6 HNO<sub>3</sub> → 2 Y(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub> + 3 H<sub>2</sub>O

